<plot>A group of five acquaintences are playing a card game. The rules are simple: take an unseen card from the previous player, then discard a card from your hand. The player who must discard the Joker is the loser. What has brought the five together, and just what stakes they are playing for, is not revealed until the end.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?278950</url></doc>
